{"tid":1784263,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"很空很空 好朋友出左pool~~~~","createTime":"2019-12-15T14:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T15:56:09.000Z","uid":301958,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c5710e903daf25c15c96455db7dde236f0a7bb4c","tid":1784263,"uid":301958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T14:20:11.000Z","msg":"最好既朋友琴日出左pool了～<br />\n平時佢日日都會wtsapp我傾計<br />\n佢多野講既程度除左wtsapp 仲會打電話黎<br />\n本身唔係一個中意傾電話既人<br />\n因為係佢 係好朋友 所以冇咩所謂<br />\n慢慢習慣左佢響身邊陪我<br />\n大家又個個星期都見 <br />\n一直都覺得單身冇咩問題<br />\n<br />\n呢2個星期佢搵少左我 <br />\n仲出埋pool <br />\n好開心佢搵到一個咁錫佢既男仔<br />\n真心登佢好開心架 亦希望佢繼續幸幸福福<br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解 就係好似少左d野咁<br />\n果種感覺 唔係傷心 而係空空地既感覺<br />\n<br />\n好朋友呀 希望你開開心心 <br />\n但唔好唔記得我呀<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻 平時覺得單身冇野既我<br />\n好似突然都有d感覺想有人陪 唉"},{"pid":"23ba2ea0abbf4fe3776821dcc7b20ff29f099b38","tid":1784263,"uid":251581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"我會記得你 你都會好快出pool"},{"pid":"57e99f4897c0485023285b47e7148e1aaf945b4a","tid":1784263,"uid":204917,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T14:22:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d27f94709f1b0596ae054ef3acbf85e18170204c","tid":1784263,"uid":301958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23ba2ea0abbf4fe3776821dcc7b20ff29f099b38","tid":1784263,"uid":251581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"我會記得你 你都會好快出pool"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T14:22:46.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3466e184241d11f9eb52d54037ff72f3699936a4","tid":1784263,"uid":301958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57e99f4897c0485023285b47e7148e1aaf945b4a","tid":1784263,"uid":204917,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5710e903daf25c15c96455db7dde236f0a7bb4c","tid":1784263,"uid":301958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T14:20:11.000Z","msg":"最好既朋友琴日出左pool了～<br />\